                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    No. Only the training certificate issued by DPR accredited MISTDO training
                                    provider will be recognized. It is the duty of any prospective trainee or
                                    customer to undertake MISTDO training at only DPR accredited training centers.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading3d">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse3d" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3d">
                                        Is there any penalty or punishment for MISTDO violations?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse3d" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading3d" data-parent="#accordion3">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Yes. Appropriate penalties/fines/sanctions in line with the Petroleum Laws and Regulations will be applied
                                    to any operator/company that violates the MISTDO program and directives.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading3c">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse3c" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3c">
                                        Who is responsible for ensuring that personnel possess MISTDO as applicable?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse3c" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading3c" data-parent="#accordion3">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    An employer (operator/company) is responsible for ensuring compliance with MISTDO
                                    requirements by all her employees.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bhoechie-tab-content">
                    <div class="accordion" id="accordion2">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2a">
                                TRAINEES Registration
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2a" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse2a">
                                        How do I register as a Trainee?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
