                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2d">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2d" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2d">
                                        Can a company carry out single or bulk registration of her employees for MISTDO training?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2d" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2d" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Yes. Companies can register single or multiple employees for any MISTDO
                                    modules/courses. However, the certificates will be issued
                                    to individuals as MISTDO training certificate is personalized.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2d">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2d" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2d">
                                        Does having MISTDO training & certificate guarantee employment?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2d" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2d" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    No. All employers have their various employment requirements.
                                    MISTDO training is only a requirement to work in the downstream operations.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2d">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2d" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2d">
                                        Can I change Training centres at any time?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2d" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2d" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Training Centers cannot be changed once training has been paid for. Trainings
                                    can only be rescheduled. A full refund of the training
                                    fee can only be obtained when the course is cancelled by the training center.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2d">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2d" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2d">
                                        I forgot my username and password?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2d" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2d" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    There is a “forgot password” link on the Trainee's Portal Login page
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2d">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2d" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2d">
                                        Can I begin a training in one training center and complete same at another training center?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2d" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2d" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    No. A Module must be completed at the training center where it was registered.
                                    You can however register to take different modules at different training centers.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2d">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2d" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2d">
                                        I cannot log on to the portal as a trainee
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2d" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2d" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Kindly verify your internet connection and your log in details.
                                    You may have put in the wrong user name or password.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2d">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2d" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2d">
                                        How do I verify that my Training Provider is accredited?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2d" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2d" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    All Training Centers on the MISTDO platform are already accredited on the OGISP platform. However, each training
                                    center has a unique ID Number which can be used for accreditation verification.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2d">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2d" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2d">
                                        Is there an age limit for registration?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2d" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2d" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Minimum age for hazardous work in Nigeria is eighteen (18) years (Source: Labour Act 2004).
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2d">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2d" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2d">
                                        Can I update my bio and any other data as a trainee?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2d" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2d" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Bio data change/update for trainees can be done at any MISTDO accredited center.
                                    It is important to have your unique ID No. for making such changes/updates.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bhoechie-tab-content">
                    <div class="accordion" id="accordion2">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2a">
                                Course/Modules
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2a" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse2a">
                                        Can I sign up for multiple modules?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>

                            <div id="collapse2a" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="heading2a" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Yes! Each trainee can enroll to more than one module and it is dependent on location, cost and availability.
                                    Note - Trainees would not be able to enroll modules simultaneously.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2b">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2b" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2b">
                                        Are there any prerequisites to enrolling on the training modules?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2b" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2b" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    There are no prerequisites for enrolling for any module on the MISTDO platform, except age requirements.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2c">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2c" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2c">
                                        How do I view the timetable for upcoming classes?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2c" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2c" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    This can be viewed by clicking the calendar tab on the MISTDO portal.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2d">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2d" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2d">
                                        What are the different types of modules or courses available on MISTDO?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2d" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2d" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Click to view modules.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bhoechie-tab-content">
                    <div class="accordion" id="accordion2">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2a">
                                Fees Payment
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2a" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse2a">
                                        How do I pay the module fees?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>

                            <div id="collapse2a" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="heading2a" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Payment of module fees is done at any DPR accredited training center of choice.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bhoechie-tab-content">
                    <div class="accordion" id="accordion2">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2a">
                                Training Certificates
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2a" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse2a">
                                        How is my training certificate issued?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>

                            <div id="collapse2a" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="heading2a" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Training certificate is issued by training centre where the module was completed.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2b">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2b" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2b">
                                        When is my training certificate issued?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2b" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2b" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Training certificate is issued at the completion of every module by the accredited training center.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2c">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2c" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2c">
                                        How long is my training certificate valid for?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2c" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2c" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Training certificate is valid for duration of two (2) years.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2d">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2d" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2d">
                                        What do I do if my training certificate is lost or stolen?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2d" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2d" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Training certificate is reissued once evidence of theft/misplacement is provided and still within its validity.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2d">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2d" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2d">
                                        How do I renew my Training certificate?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2d" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2d" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Training certificate can be renewed by registering for a refresher course on or before the expiry of the present certificate.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2d">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2d" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2d">
                                        Are there fees for certificate renewal?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2d" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2d" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Yes, there are fees for training certificate renewal.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2d">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2d" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2d">
                                        Is renewal of certificate mandatory?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2d" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2d" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Yes, renewal of training certificate is mandatory if the holder must continue
                                    work in the Downstream sector of the oil and gas industry
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>


                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bhoechie-tab-content">
                    <div class="accordion" id="accordion2">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2a">
                                    TRAINING PROVIDERS	Registration
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2a" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse2a">
                                          How do I register as a Training Provider?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>

                            <div id="collapse2a" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="heading2a" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Training Providers are required to register and apply for MISTDO Permit listed under Specialized Category on the OGISP Portal. 
                                    If permit is granted, training providers may log on to MISTDO portal with the permit number.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2b">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2b" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2b">
                                        How much does it cost to register as a training provider on MISTDO?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2b" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2b" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    N250, 000:00 for MISTDO Permit (OGISP).
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2c">
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2c" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2c">
                                        What are the requirements needed to be a Training Provider?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2c" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2c" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Download the requirements.

                                    Note: Accreditation assessment shall be conducted, and only qualified
                                    training centers shall be accredited to offer trainings in line with standardized 
                                    requirements. Thereafter, the same permitting/accreditation process shall apply annually.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="heading2a">
                                Fees Payment
                                <h5 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2a" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse2a">
                                        Are there renewal fees for Training Providers?
                                    </button>
                                </h5>
                            </div>

                            <div id="collapse2a" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="heading2a" data-parent="#accordion2">
                                <div class="card-body text-justify">
                                    Yes. Accreditation for training providers is valid for one (1) year and a fee is applicable for renewal.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

